      "side": 1,
      "message": "Got it:\n\nprogram() runs the steps to see that we \"can\" fit in bytes, but doesn\u0027t do anything with the values.\n\nuniforms() runs each time we \"refresh\" the uniforms for a given (re)use of the program, and shoves the (premuled in dst colorspace) value into the uniform slot.",
      "parentUuid": "2e7bc5b9_8cce5c7e",
